Name: Auro The Bunny
About the game: Auro The Bunny is a game in which you'll control a rabbit who'll have to collect the fruits he finds along the way, avoiding obstacles such as saws, scythes and even lava. Are you ready for this challenge? This game includes: - Three distinct scenarios - Several Obstacles such as Saws, Sickles and even Lava - Many Challenges - Beautiful Soundtrack
